    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prepare to keep (or lose) your temper online! </strong><br>Play solo, with friends or online multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This beloved game classic offers even more game options: “<strong>Ludo XXL 2</strong>” brings the crazy dice-rolling fun straight to your living room – or, with the latest online multiplayer mode, even to Grandma and Grandpa on the other side of the world. This game guarantees laughter, dice-rolling, and (of course!) the occasional friendly flare-up of frustration. Enjoy a colorful mix of unpredictable good fortune and hilarity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This <strong>evergreen board game</strong> has been reissued for those who can't get enough playful frustration in their lives!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online dice fun</strong>: Play with friends and family around the globe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety guaranteed: <strong>8 beautifully designed game boards</strong>, including 4 new ones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Three game modes</strong>, heated duels: Classic, Extra, and Extreme.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable rules</strong>: Play anyway you like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 6 players</strong>: Exciting matches for all ages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum flexibility: <strong>Locally</strong> or <strong>online</strong>, with real players or against AI.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323580/extras/d4aa222ee2192578459c6c100ce5a7a6.avif?t=1765101263\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323580/extras_big/d4aa222ee2192578459c6c100ce5a7a6.webp?t=1765101263 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p>",
